query.esql:
from logs-corelight.ssl-*
| limit 10000
| where event.dataset == "tls" and observer.vendor == "Corelight" and ssl.validation_status == "self signed certificate" and observer.hostname is not null
| stats count_distinct(destination.domain)
| rename `count_distinct(destination.domain)` as `Self Signed Certs`

from logs-corelight.ssl-*
| limit 10000
| where event.dataset == "tls" and observer.vendor == "Corelight" and ssl.validation_status == "self signed certificate" and observer.hostname is not null
| stats count_distinct(destination.domain)
| rename `count_distinct(destination.domain)` as `Self Signed Certs`

from logs-corelight.x509-*
| limit 10000
| where observer.vendor == "Corelight" and event.dataset == "x509" and observer.hostname is not null and file.x509.not_after is not null
| eval not_valid_after = to_datetime(file.x509.not_after),current_time = to_datetime(now())
| eval days_to_expire = date_diff("day", not_valid_after,current_time)
| where days_to_expire > 0 and days_to_expire <= 15
| stats count_distinct(file.hash.sha256)
| rename `count_distinct(file.hash.sha256)` as `Expiring Certs.`
| keep `Expiring Certs.`

from logs-corelight.x509-*
| limit 10000
| where observer.vendor == "Corelight" and event.dataset == "x509" and observer.hostname is not null and file.x509.not_after is not null
| eval not_valid_after = to_datetime(file.x509.not_after),current_time = to_datetime(now())
| eval days_to_expire = date_diff("day", not_valid_after,current_time)
| where days_to_expire > 0 and days_to_expire <= 15
| stats count_distinct(file.hash.sha256)
| rename `count_distinct(file.hash.sha256)` as `Expiring Certs.`
| keep `Expiring Certs.`

query.esql:
from logs-corelight.conn-*
| limit 10000
| where observer.vendor == "Corelight" and event.dataset == "conn" and observer.hostname is not null and network.protocol == "dns"
| where conn.local_resp == "true"
| where destination.ip IS NOT NULL AND destination.port IN (53, 5353)
| stats count_distinct(destination.ip)
| rename `count_distinct(destination.ip)` as `Internal DNS Servers`

query.esql:
from logs-corelight.various-*
| limit 10000
| where observer.vendor == "Corelight" and event.dataset == "vpn" and observer.hostname is not null
| stats count() by @timestamp
| rename `count()` as count
| keep count,@timestamp
